rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0001
rows.name:
I can't believe this...
Are we going to have to cancel
negotiations now?

rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Some Lysaat found their way into our
cargo hold, would you believe it.

rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0003
rows.name:
We were supposed to be starting
business talks, but I can't exactly
send the ship out now...

rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I asked Avaritia security to sort it
out, but they got scared and ran off!

rows.label: tlk41300012_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Now that, my friends, would be
absolutely pukka. You look like
you could handle them.
